### [Exodus Chapter 37](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#001.md)

[Exodus 37:1](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_001">exo 37:1</span></span>

Preparation of the vessels of the dwelling: viz., the ark of the
covenant ([Exo 37:1-9](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#001.md), as in [Exo
25:10-22](../../../bib/kjv/exo025.htm#010).md); the table of shew-bread and
its vessels ([Exo 37:10-16](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#010.md), as in [Exo
25:23-30](../../../bib/kjv/exo025.htm#023).md); the candlestick ([Exo
37:17-24](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#017.md), as in [Exo
25:31-40](../../../bib/kjv/exo025.htm#031).md); the altar of incense ([Exo
37:25-28](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#025.md), as in [Exo
30:1-10](../../../bib/kjv/exo030.htm#001).md); the anointing oil and
incense ([Exo 37:29](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#029).md), directions for
the preparation of which are given in Ex 30:22-38; the altar of
burnt-offering ([Exo 38:1-7](../../../bib/kjv/exo038.htm#001.md), as in
[Exo 27:1-8](../../../bib/kjv/exo027.htm#001).md); the laver ([Exo
37:8](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#008.md), as in [Exo
30:17-21](../../../bib/kjv/exo030.htm#017).md); and the court ([Exo
37:9-20](../../../bib/kjv/exo037.htm#009.md), as in [Exo
27:9-19](../../../bib/kjv/exo027.htm#009).md). The order corresponds on the
whole to the list of the separate articles in [Exo
35:11-19](../../../bib/kjv/exo035.htm#011.md), and to the construction of
the entire sanctuary; but the holy chest (the ark), as being the most
holy thing of all, is distinguished above all the rest, by being
expressly mentioned as the work of Bezaleel, the chief architect of the
whole.

